<br />\n香港時間22時44分"},{"pid":"5b28f0873f75f9557caa9c9941d638c3384d4bec","tid":1712644,"uid":51696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T15:04:40.000Z","msg":"手動轉<br />\n以下係假校巴<br />\n最少6架 全車都係口罩扮示威者<br />\n請傳開叫學生小心!<br />\n<br />\n1721 #大學站 停車<br />\nUz7425 灰色Honda<br />\nUr4357 藍灰萬事得<br />\nVp4735 深藍 萬事得<br />\nPC 4766<br />\n全便衣狗 帶口罩 大學站停車<br />\n<br />\n#中大 吐露港，近大埔南出口<br />\nUR7325<br />\nNA6183<br />\nUJ5467<br />\n<br />\n1737 赤泥坪巴士站 假校巴 TR5476 白色現代私家車<br />\n<br />\n#自行判斷 #自己小心<br />\n1"},{"pid":"8d44012f287c932e7ed100073afc33291657ce30","tid":1712644,"uid":261995,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T15:05:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/eibUFCZ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FeibUFCZ.jpg&h=a97ba1f0&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}